    FSController -->|creates| CronJob

    AuthModule -->|creates| RBAC["Roles / RoleBindings<br/>ClusterRoles / ClusterRoleBindings"]
    NSRegistry -->|maintains| ConfigRegistry["feast-configs-registry<br/>ConfigMap"]

    NotebookCR["Kubeflow Notebook<br/>(with feast-integration label)"] -->|watched by| NBController
