    OnlineStore -->|optional| ExtDB["External Databases<br/>(PostgreSQL, Redis, Snowflake)"]
    OfflineStore -->|optional| ExtDB
    Registry -->|optional| ObjStore["S3 / GCS<br/>Object Stores"]

    UIServer -->|exposed via| Route["OpenShift Route<br/>(Reencrypt TLS)"]

    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes| MetricsSvc["Metrics Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS"]

